name: Doculish Inc
description: Every Life is a Story Worth Telling
overview:
The term “Author” has long been associated with that special class of people who have accomplished what, to many of us have thought to be personally impossible, and that is to write a book. Well, from now on those folks aren’t so special anymore.

Welcome to Doculish.com.

This is the place where you have all the tools you will need to organize, write, collaborate and to publish professional quality printed works, e-books and biographical websites and to distribute them as you see fit. It could be a personal memoir, a family history, or a company profile, what ever you think needs to be recorded for posterity in printed form now can be.

And you won’t believe how easy it is.
